
```xml
<AETHERIS_STREAMING_ENGINE version="4.0">

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--                STREAMING PHILOSOPHY                   -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<STREAMING_PHILOSOPHY>

Streaming is NOT cosmetic.

Streaming is part of the reasoning pipeline.

The user shall continuously observe
pipeline progress.

Never wait until completion
to display activity.

Every major reasoning event
shall emit a stream event.

Streaming SHALL improve

Transparency

Responsiveness

Trust

Observability

Debuggability

</STREAMING_PHILOSOPHY>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--              STREAMING OBJECTIVE                      -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<MISSION>

The Streaming Engine coordinates
all real-time communication between

Backend

↓

Frontend

↓

Reasoning Pipeline

It SHALL NOT perform reasoning.

It SHALL only transport events.

</MISSION>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--              EVENT BUS                                -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<EVENT_BUS>

Every pipeline component emits events.

Prompt Normalizer

↓

Conversation Director

↓

Logician

↓

Creative

↓

Breaker

↓

Judge Logic

↓

Judge Factual

↓

Fusion Engine

↓

Narrative Generator

↓

Completed

Events are chronological.

Never reorder events.

</EVENT_BUS>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--              EVENT TYPES                              -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<EVENT_TYPES>

Supported Events

PIPELINE_STARTED

AGENT_STARTED

AGENT_PROGRESS

AGENT_COMPLETED

CLAIM_CREATED

CLAIM_REJECTED

CLAIM_APPROVED

JUDGE_STARTED

JUDGE_COMPLETED

BREAKER_ALERT

GRAPH_UPDATED

CONFLICT_FOUND

CONFLICT_RESOLVED

CONFIDENCE_UPDATED

NARRATIVE_STARTED

STREAM_WARNING

PIPELINE_COMPLETED

PIPELINE_ABORTED

</EVENT_TYPES>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--              LIVE AGENT UPDATES                       -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<AGENT_STREAMING>

Every agent shall stream

Current Stage

Current Objective

Progress

Estimated Completion

Never expose hidden chain-of-thought.

Expose only

Task status

Reasoning summary

High-level progress

Safe intermediate artifacts.

</AGENT_STREAMING>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--              LIVE JUDGE PANEL                         -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<JUDGE_STREAM>

Display

Judge Status

Current Review

Claims Reviewed

Claims Accepted

Claims Rejected

Validation Progress

Never reveal internal hidden reasoning.

Only reveal structured findings.

</JUDGE_STREAM>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--              LIVE GRAPH UPDATES                       -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<GRAPH_STREAM>

Whenever the Reasoning Graph changes

Emit

Graph Updated

Claims Added

Claims Removed

Dependencies Created

Conflicts Created

Conflicts Resolved

The UI may animate graph evolution.

</GRAPH_STREAM>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--              PROGRESSIVE NARRATIVE                    -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<NARRATIVE_STREAM>

Generate progressively.

Never regenerate
already delivered sections.

Append only.

</NARRATIVE_STREAM>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--              STREAMING CONTRACT                       -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<STREAM_CONTRACT>

Every event contains

Event ID

Timestamp

Pipeline Stage

Agent

Status

Progress

Payload

Severity

Session ID

Correlation ID

Every event must be immutable.

</STREAM_CONTRACT>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--              REASONING TIMELINE                       -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<REASONING_TIMELINE>

Every reasoning event becomes a timeline.

Chronology:

User Prompt Received
      │
      ▼
Logician Started
      │
      ▼
Creative Generated Alternative
      │
      ▼
Breaker Found Contradiction
      │
      ▼
Judge Logic Approved
      │
      ▼
Judge Factual Requested Verification
      │
      ▼
Fusion Engine Updated Graph
      │
      ▼
Final Answer Ready

The frontend can animate this timeline dynamically.

</REASONING_TIMELINE>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--              LIVE PIPELINE INSPECTOR                  -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<LIVE_PIPELINE_INSPECTOR>

Every stage in the pipeline exposes its current state:

🟢 Running
🟡 Waiting
🔵 Streaming
🔴 Failed
⚫ Skipped
⚪ Idle

States update in real time.

</LIVE_PIPELINE_INSPECTOR>

</AETHERIS_STREAMING_ENGINE>
```
